Sophia Anna Bush -LRB- born July 8 , 1982 -RRB- is an American actress , director , spokesperson , and activist .
She starred in The WB/CW drama series One Tree Hill , where she played Brooke Davis from 2003 to 2012 .
She is known for her film roles in John Tucker Must Die -LRB- 2006 -RRB- , The Hitcher -LRB- 2007 -RRB- , and The Narrows -LRB- 2008 -RRB- .
She starred in the NBC police procedural drama series Chicago P.D. as Det. Erin Lindsay .